<sect1 id="dir_b670ef0f6850d7b2892f5d96e38a12a4_1autotoc_md215">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::health</title><para>Health management system for game entities.</para>
<para>This module provides components, events, and systems for tracking entity health, processing damage, and handling death.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_b670ef0f6850d7b2892f5d96e38a12a4_1autotoc_md216">
<title>Submodules</title><para><table rows="4" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Submodule  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Purpose  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>components/</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Health-related ECS components  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>events/</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Health-related events (death)  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>systems/</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Systems for health processing  </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_b670ef0f6850d7b2892f5d96e38a12a4_1autotoc_md217">
<title>Architecture</title><para>1. <bold>HealthComponent</bold> tracks current and maximum health 2. <bold>Combat systems</bold> call <computeroutput>takeDamage()</computeroutput> when damage is dealt 3. <bold>HealthUpdateSystem</bold> detects <computeroutput>health &lt;= 0</computeroutput> and:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Issues <computeroutput>DespawnCommand</computeroutput> to remove the entity</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Publishes <computeroutput>DeathEvent</computeroutput> for other systems (e.g., scoring)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_b670ef0f6850d7b2892f5d96e38a12a4_1autotoc_md218">
<title>Integration</title><para>The health system integrates with:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><bold>Combat system</bold> - receives damage via <computeroutput>takeDamage()</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Scoring system</bold> - <computeroutput>DeathEvent</computeroutput> triggers score awards</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Spawn system</bold> - dead entities are despawned via command</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
